<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.1">
<l>nummait toḻutōm nuntam paṇicey tirukkum nummaṭiyōm</l>
<l>immaik kiṉpam peṟṟō mentā yinta ḷūrīrē</l>
<l>emmaik kaṭitāk karuma maruḷi yāvā veṉṟiraṅki</l>
<l>nammai yorukāl kāṭṭi naṭantāl nāṅka ḷuyyōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We adore you; we, your servants, who are doing homage to only you,</l>
<l>Gained delight in this life, our father, you of Intaḷūr.</l>
<l>Granting us [good] karma soon, pitying [us], saying, “Ah! Ah!”</l>
<l>If [you] proceed [here] revealing [yourself] to us one time, won’t we be saved?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
